  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl93_LabelType\">You have a way with calming tempers, using cool logic to sooth heated disagreements, and you were always the one to settle arguments among your friends, family, and community.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl93_LabelType\">You receive a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks. In addition, you receive a +1 trait bonus to the DC of any charm or compulsion effect that does not provide ongoing control and results in peaceful acts, such as <em>calm emotions</em>, <em>sleep</em>, or a <em>suggestion </em>to lay down arms.</span></p>",
